data.value:
- Fixing bugs in the Windows Classic (Win32UI) previewer
- Quick Apply Colors in Win32UI Editor, instead of loading into palette and applying.
- Retro Themes Presets (from Windows 3.1, Windows 98 and Windows Classic (2000/XP)), The presets are usable in Windows Classic (Win32UI) Editor and Color Picker
